## Migration Guides

### Migrating from v1.x to v2.0

Due to the significant changes in v2.0, we've created a detailed [Migration Guide](docs/migration-v2.md) to help you upgrade smoothly.

Key migration steps:
1. Update CSS class names to new BEM convention
2. Update JavaScript API calls to new manager-based system
3. Update CSS custom property names
4. Test accessibility features with new ARIA implementations

